{
  "stem": "15540.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But these pick-ups of cabs coming and going out in the country was not exactly something that, that was normal.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So it was a very dangerous situation, and you never knew whether the cab drivers could be trusted or not.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we were brought back into a city, and we stayed in a hotel for a couple of hours.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they brought food up to the rooms.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They didn't think we should sit in the restaurant and be seen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And at this point, this friend of my uncle's came and announced that he was buying a boat for my father to sail it, because he couldn't find anybody who could do it.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my mother said that we might as well go to Germany, because there was no way my father could sail a boat.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He knew nothing about boats.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she refused.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then a little later, somebody came and said they had a boat that night.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we were ordered to walk out to this very landing, which was about a five-mile walk from the city.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that I still can see very clearly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I can see us walking down this country road with our small suitcases.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was in the middle of the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, it was so--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we walked, we walked some miles apart.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But still, it was not a very usual suit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We also-- a usual sight.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We also had a lot of clothes on, because my mother had put, you know, two sets of coats and two sets of everything, because it was the only way we could bring something along.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were very warm at this point.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we came out to this beach, where we, where we hid in some bushes.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
